Isiraeli to Oldoinyo le Sinai


1  Ore te nkolong e dukuya olapa li okuni anaa pee epuo iltung'ana loo Siraeli te nkop e Misiri, ore ina olong nepuonu olpurkel le Sinai. 
2  Ore pee edumunye te Refidim aapuonu olpurkel le Sinai neitayu ilng'oborri to lpurkel; ore te ine nepik Isiraeli ilng'oborri dukuya o ldoinyo. 
3  Neked Musa alo enetii Enkai, neipot ninye Olaitoriani to ldoinyo, ejo, “Ena iyie ilo ajoki enkaji e Yakobo, niliki iltung'ana loo Siraeli: ajoki, 
4  Itoduaa intae enaikuna Ilmisiri, ina natanapa nanu intae too naipuko o lkurragos nayaki intae kewan ai. 
5   Ore naa taata tinining'ining'i oltoilo lai nimbung'ubung'u nkitanapat o sotua lai, niaakuku iltung'ana laainei tukul ti atua iltung'ana pooki; amu ore enkop pooki naa enaai, 
6   naa iakuku intae te nanu enkitoria oo lapolosak o losho osinya. Kulo ninche irorei lilo ajoki nkera e Israel.”


7  Nelotu Musa neipot lelo payiani loo ltung'ana, neibalie te dukuya ninche kulo rorei pooki ooitanapa Olaitoriani ninye. 
8  Newal iltung'ana pooki te nebo nejo, “Ore nena pooki naatejo Olaitoriani eikiaas.” Nelikioo Musa irorei loo ltung'ana to Laitoriani. 
9  Nejoki Olaitoriani Musa, “Ng'ura, kalotu nanu te nkatampoi nairrusha, pee etum iltung'ana aatoning te naairorie iyie, pee kitum sii aairuko ntarasi.”

Neitoki Musa aliki Olaitoriani irorei loo ltung'ana. 
10  Nejoki Olaitoriani Musa, “Shomo enetii iltung'ana nintisiny ninche taata o taisere, nincho ninche meisuja inkilani enye, 
11  nerretena te nkolong e uni; amu ore te nkolong e uni nelotu Olaitoriani adou enchumata o ldoinyo le Sinai metoduaa iltung'ana. 
12   Nipikaki iltung'ana olpolosie aitamanaa, ijo, ‘Entodol ake mipuopuo shumata o ldoinyo arashu iseyieyie olpolosie lenye; ore pooki ng'ae ororo oldoinyo neari metua. 
13  Nemeetae enkaina naiseyie ninye kake kenang'i too soito arashu eng'ori, aa eng'ues arashu oltung'ani, melo ninye eishu.’ Ore pee eru entarumpeta ayiataa, naa keilepu ninche aapuonu oldoinyo.” 
14  Nedou Musa to ldoinyo alotu enetii iltung'ana, neitisiny ninye iltung'ana neisuj ninche inkilani enye. 
15  Nejoki ninye iltung'ana, “Enterretenata te nkolong e uni, nimipuopuo aanyikaki nkituaak. 
16   Ore takedenya te nkolong e uni, netii ndarat o nkiwuang'at, o enkatampoi nairrusha e nchumata oldoinyio, o endarata sapuk e ntarumpeta, o metaa einkirikirate iltung'ana pooki ootii ilng'oborri. 
17  Neyau Musa iltung'ana aitung'uaa ilng'oborri meetu aatumore Enkai; neitashe ninche te ntonata o ldoinyo. 
18  Neimulumul oldoinyo le Sinai empuruo, amu etadoikio Olaitoriani enchumata enye te nkima, neilep empuruo enye anaa empuruo o lkokuet, neikirikira oldoinyo pooki oleng. 
19  Naa ore anaa enadaru embuakunoto e ntarumpeta aponari, neiro Musa, newaliki ninye Enkai te ndarata. 
20  Nelotu Olaitoriani adoiki oldoinyo le Sinai, entopij o ldoinyo; neipot Olaitoriani Musa meshomo entopij o ldoinyo, neilep Musa alo. 
21  Nejoki Olaitoriani Musa, “Tadoi shomo inkoo iltung'ana, melang'u ake olpolosie memuta ake ilkumok lenye. 
22  Nchoo sii lelo apolosak oonyikaki Olaitoriani eitisiny ate, pee maitame ake ninche.” 
23  Nejoki Musa Olaitoriani, “Mepuonu iltung'ana aailepu oldoinyo le Sinai; amu iyie enkorrok ino oitanapa iyiook, ajo, ‘Entayu ilpolosien to ldoinyo, nintisinyinyi ninye.’ ” 
24  Nejoki Olaitoriani ninye “Tadoi shomo pee ilepu ayau Aron te nebo iyie; kake mincho ilapolosak o ltung'ana elang'u olpolosie aailepu enetii Olaitoriani menang'are ake Olaitoriani ninche.” 
25  Nelo Musa adoyio enetii iltung'ana neliki ninche.

